result.execSummary:
The defendant Victoria Ayla Nava was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Victoria Ayla Nava is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Victoria Ayla Nava was found guilty of Possession of THC, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
